{
  "stem": "13524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When there was [GERMAN], when there was a transport, who was not young enough, or not fit for work, they were shooting en masse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also heard, like, when parents were discussing that people were being hanged in ghetto, and how they were saying, [NON-ENGLISH], at the last moment, at the gallows.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people praying-- yes-- to God, in that-- in that terrible moment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, my parents held everything in secret from the children, not to upset us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think my parents must have been convinced that if they behave justly, if they will do what the Germans are telling us to do, we will survive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war will pass.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was just the beginning of most horrible era.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, later on, a whole transports of people were taken out of ghetto into Treblinka, into Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were people-- Poles-- aware that the people were taken there, shot, or they had to dig their own graves before they were shot, and then just shot in such a way that they fell into the grave.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were two, three Poles to cover this thing up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the stories trickled down to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But who wanted to believe the Germans would do this sort of thing for no reason, especially when they were telling us that they're taking them to village because-- all sorts of reasons?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The children were going to orphanage, it was told.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some parents felt, well, they will be better off than in ghetto, where there is no food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow, nobody wanted to give their children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody wanted to go onto the transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were forced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was always SS, with guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the resistance, slightest resistance, you were shot-- left in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
